{"tid":1756494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人啟事 暴大電單車巴","createTime":"2019-11-26T05:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T10:48:02.000Z","uid":256131,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45865f25d53518bdbf71d04fb534211caff74d2c","tid":1756494,"uid":256131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"暴大secret見到<br />\n點解我無呢d夢境<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電單車型到cls<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//11月12號晚<br />\n暴大極需要人個日<br />\n好不容易行到暴大幫手<br />\n到凌晨3點半先走<br />\n好多謝個位鐵騎士車我走<br />\n如果唔係已經打算同我fd行兩三個鐘番屋企<br />\n我想講原來坐電單車真係好好玩<br />\n個十五分鐘既路程洗走左一晚既疲累<br />\n如果你記得我的話<br />\n我想問你有無女朋友<br />\n如果無既話光復之日可唔可以比我追你<br />\n好後悔個刻無問你拎電話<br />\n怕騎劫左成個意義<br />\n同埋怕大家都有防備心//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2368863893217712?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F376586225778832%2Fposts%2F2368863893217712%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9c6e287d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2368863893217712?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"72e164d8e26dcb2d56a1725bf498018784835f75","tid":1756494,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5WrRAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5WrRAW.jpg&h=56181f3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"986ecee0739de1d3131c102dec3e57c24728d2c5","tid":1756494,"uid":108285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"人生雖短暫 無悔共你<br />\n穿梭天邊與海岸<br />\n重溫的景象 零碎漸淡<br />\n真心你莫忘記"},{"pid":"ada0cfd31e96bd85508d7f02e9f9406d773f8522","tid":1756494,"uid":